1988年12月，[[联合国教科文组织|联合国教科文组织]]将部分区域列入[[世界遗产|世界遗产]]名录<ref name=whsselection>{{Citation   | contribution = Report of the 世界遗产委员会 Twelfth Session   | contribution-url = http://whc.unesco.org/archive/repcom88.htm#119   | series = Convention Concerning the Protection of the World Cultural and Natural Heritage   | year = 1988   | place = Brasilia   | publisher = UNESCO   | url = http://whc.unesco.org/archive/repcom88.htm   | title = UNITED NATIONS EDUCATIONAL, SCIENTIFIC AND CULTURAL ORGANIZATION - CONVENTION CONCERNING THE PROTECTION OF THE WORLD CULTURAL AND NATURAL HERITAGE - Report of the World Heritage Committee - Twelfth Session   | accessdate = 2019-01-16   | archive-date = 2012-01-29   | archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/652wVFRF0?url=http://whc.unesco.org/archive/repcom88.htm   | dead-url = no   }}</ref>，{{世界遗产基准|2|4|5}}

在此之前的1979年，由于缺乏恰当的划界，联合国教科文组织未批准申请<ref name=ICOMOS>{{Cite web   | last = [[国际纪念碑及遗址委员会|国际纪念碑及遗址委员会]]   | title = Advisory Body Evaluation of Timbuktu Nomination   | publisher = UNESCO   | date = 1979-05-14   | url = http://whc.unesco.org/archive/advisory_body_evaluation/119.pdf   | accessdate = 2011-02-22   | archive-date = 2016-08-19   | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160819204840/http://whc.unesco.org/archive/advisory_body_evaluation/119.pdf   | dead-url = no   }}</ref>。1990年至2005年，曾列入[[濒危世界遗产|濒危世界遗产]]名录。

== 流行文化 ==
欧美人士常将廷巴克图（Timbuktu）想象为神秘之地。在2006年一项对英国青年人的调查中，34%并不认为廷巴克图是真实存在的，其余66%则认为廷巴克图是一个神话般的地方<ref name=BBC_twin>{{citation | title = Search on for Timbuktu's twin | publisher = BBC News | date = 2006-10-18 | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/6062360.stm | accessdate = 2010-11-22 | archive-date = 2021-03-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210309192304/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/6062360.stm | dead-url = no }}</ref>。在英语词典中，“廷巴克图”一词至少从1863年起即已成为“遥不可及之地”的[[隐喻|隐喻]]<ref>{{cite web| title = Entry on 'Timbuktu'| work = Online Etymology Dictionary| publisher = Douglas Harper| year = 2002| url = http://www.etymonline.com/index.php?search=timbuktu&searchmode=none| accessdate = 2010-09-17| archive-date = 2016-03-04| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304043648/http://www.etymonline.com/index.php?search=timbuktu&searchmode=none| dead-url = no}}</ref>，廷巴克图也因为遥远这一特性而出现在部分影视作品中。1970年[[华特迪士尼影片|华特迪士尼影片]]动画电影《[[猫儿历险记|猫儿历险记]]》中，管家艾吉试图将主人家里的几只猫送到廷巴克图，但自己反而被装箱运走，此片亦误将廷巴克图标记为[[法屬赤道非洲|法屬赤道非洲]]属地，而非[[法屬西非|法屬西非]]属地<ref>[http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0065421/goofs Notes on ''The Aristocats''] {{Wayback|url=http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0065421/goofs |date=20160105113817 }}. [[互联网电影数据库|互联网电影数据库]].</ref>。廷巴克图也是1959年电影《{{link-en|廷巴克图 (1959年电影)|Timbuktu (1959 film)|廷巴克图}}》和2014年电影《[[廷巴克图_(电影)|廷巴克图]]》的故事背景。

